window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>USA Today bestselling author, Jane Anthony, delivers an emotionally raw &amp; intense tale of passion, heartache, and love. Sit ringside while Jace Wilder—a bad boy MMA Fighter &amp; Hell's Bend High's biggest bully—dukes it out with Ellie Cartwright—a sheltered good girl with nothing left to lose—on their bumpy road to happily ever after.</p> <p>Brutal bully. Hotter than hell. MMA God.</p> <p>Jace Wilder owns Hell's Bend High and everyone in it. Everyone except me that is. The girls love him, the guys want to be him . . . I just want to stay away from him.</p> <p>But when the death of my mother forces me into the Wilder home, I become his latest target. Only, I can't tell if he wants to torment me or take me to bed.</p> <p>He may think I'm easy prey, a poor little rich girl down on her luck, but looks can be deceiving. I can give as good as I get, and Jace Wilder will never see me coming.</p> <p>Contains mature themes.</p>"; 
